name: Digital Fire Truck #01
description: My name is Léo, I'm 6 years old and I like to draw, paint, play the drums, dance breaking, sing, play video games and I really want to have a dog. Since I was little I am in love with fire trucks. This is my first drawing done with a graphics tablet in photoshop, I am still trying to adapt ... it is also my first NFT. "PNG 6000 x 3600 px"
